arch:property.oc:show_val: Medium-size unit, variety of sizes, taxa, elements. Fair amount of cattle, including a sizable pile of horn core crumbles. Although some large pieces, generally quite fragmented. Even most of the phalanges are broken. All teeth are uppers. Last number = 156

arch:string.div: The unique identifier for each contextual unit, matching those used in the central Çatalhöyük excavation database and in publications. The excavation uses single-context recording.
